Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Gary Hart confesses
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0440lht
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Dec 1987
Republican glee as voters see Senator Hart's confession of affairs as a serious character flaw. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less